full_text:
What is the Hospital Readmissions Reduction Program (or HRRP)?

Goal is to incentivize hospitals to reduce readmissions among Medicare patients by penalizing general acute care hospitals having higher-than-anticipated 30-day risk-adjusted readmission rates over prior 3 years https://t.co/Yc7n6YLFR5
